t:
During the winter, finding names  
written on the snow is pretty          
common around here.                   



But I'm unsure what kind of            
strange name ‘EM PLEH’ is,         
written on the ice in this frozen       
lake.
c:
I scratch the surface of the ice making it impossible for anyone else to read.
